def transform_dataset(test_list):
    # Flatten the input list of lists into a single list
    flattened = [item for sublist in test_list for item in sublist]
    
    # Wrap the flattened list in another list to match the desired output format
    output = [flattened]
    
    # Print the output
    print(output)
    
    return output
